Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20when%20he%20didn't%20do%20his%20homework%20and%20his%20grades%20tanked%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20take%20him%20to%20meet%20someone%20to%20possibly%20buy%20or%20sell%20an%20item%20until%20he%20had%20zero%20missed%20school%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explained%20that%20those%20requirements%20also%20occur%20in%20life.%20If%20you%2C%20as%20a%20business%20owner%2C%20don't%20file%20your%20taxes%2C%20it%20reaches%20the%20point%20where%20you%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20operate%20until%20you%20bring%20your%20outstanding%20taxes%20up%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20constant%20struggle%E2%80%94school%20and%20his%20business%E2%80%94but%20I%20stayed%20the%20course.%20Then%2C%20one%20day%2C%20he%20told%20me%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20graduate%20from%20high%20school%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinishing%20school%20meant%20more%20freedom%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20he%20loved%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20he'd%20have%20to%20buckle%20down%20and%20really%20apply%20himself%20academically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20school%20aligned%20with%20his%20goals%2C%20he%20engaged%20for%20good.%20He%20completed%20his%20coursework%20and%20graduated%20six%20months%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%20I%20was%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220987df1a-8b21-49ca-b060-9242d81b3308%5C%22%3EI%20stayed%20consistent%20so%20he%20could%20make%20a%20different%20choice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20at%2018%2C%20my%20son%20lives%20at%20home%20and%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbegged-daughter-live-home-college-dorm-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20knows%20he%20doesn't%20enjoy%20traditional%20learning%20and%20the%20traditional%20academic%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20consider%20his%20graduating%20early%20a%20huge%20win%E2%80%94not%20only%20because%20we%20saw%20how%20easily%20he%20completed%20his%20coursework%2C%20but%20also%20because%20we%20now%