ed%20the%20HIMARS%20as%20a%20key%20weapon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstonia%20received%20six%20HIMARS%20in%20April%2C%20Latvia%20has%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20US%20for%20six%20of%20the%20systems%2C%20expected%20by%202027%2C%20and%20Lithuania%20is%20purchasing%20eight%20of%20them%2C%20with%20the%20first%20deliveries%20expected%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20countries%20see%20the%20deep%20strike%20capability%20as%20critical%20based%20on%20watching%20Ukraine.%20Hanno%20Pevkur%2C%20Estonia's%20defense%20minister%2C%20explained%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20country%20believes%20the%20combat-tested%20HIMARS%20send%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeterrence%20message%26quot%3B%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20long%20strike%20capability%2C%20deep%20strike%20capability%20in%20Estonia%20already%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22803be399-9d9a-4162-875e-f641951e9ee3%5C%22%3EUkraine%20shows%20the%20need%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20lessons%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20robust%20air%20defenses%2C%20deep%20ammunition%20stockpiles%2C%20and%20strong%20electronic%20warfare%20capabilities%2C%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20ability%20to%20strike%20deep%20behind%20enemy%20lines%20or%20into%20hostile%20territory%20is%20essential%2C%20Pevkur%20said.%20The%20HIMARS%20deliver%20that%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ukraine%20first%20received%20HIMARS%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Russian%20ammo%20depots%2C%20command%20and%20control%20centers%2C%20and%20more%20that%20had%20been%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20Ukrainian%20artillery%20were%20suddenly%20vulnerable.%20The%20Guided%20Multiple%20Launch%20Rocket%20System%20had%20the%20reach%20needed%20to%20strike%20critical%20Russian%20targets.%20These%20surface-to-surface%20rockets%20have%20a%20range%20of%20around%2070%20kilometers%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20put%20them%20to%20use%20battering%20tactically%20significant%20Russian%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifical