ce%20you're%20in%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20get%20out%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Ogan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265fe7c41-d6df-4a35-a032-2813267f47e5%5C%22%3ELosing%20ground%20on%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELei%20Xing%20said%20that%20while%20Tesla%20was%20still%20the%20%26quot%3Bbenchmark%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20Chinese%20automakers%20in%20terms%20of%20tech%2C%20the%20US%20firm%20was%20now%20behind%20on%20some%20key%20features%2C%20such%20as%20advanced%20driver%20assistance%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20previously%20said%20that%20Tesla's%20attempts%20to%20launch%20its%20Full%20Self-Driving%20system%20have%20been%20hampered%20by%20Chinese%20rules%20around%20data%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20launched%20a%20limited%20version%20of%20FSD%20in%20China%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20but%20it%20charges%20Tesla%20owners%20around%20%248%2C000%20to%20access%20it%2C%20unlike%20many%20of%20its%20rivals%2C%20who%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-self-driving-expansion-cheap-seagull-ev-high-level-features-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebegun%20offering%20similar%20systems%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20ADAS%2C%20because%20of%20some%20of%20the%20regulatory%20restrictions%2C%20Tesla%20is%20behind%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lei%20Xing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20features%20are%20becoming%20commoditized.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-cheap-ev-seagull-coming-to-europe-china-us-tariffs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBYD%20Seagull%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20highway%20ADAS%20as%20standard.%20Customers%20have%20come%20to%20expect%20these%20kinds%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teslas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686e698d85e81483682da36d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223956%5C%22%3