ght%20on%20how%20Amazon%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20these%20endeavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%2C%20from%20late%202024%2C%20describes%20a%20project%2C%20codenamed%20Starfish%2C%20that%20uses%20AI%20models%20to%20%26quot%3Bsynthesize%26quot%3B%20information%20from%20various%20data%20sources%2C%20such%20as%20external%20websites%20and%20images.%20It%20then%20generates%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%2C%20correct%2C%20and%20consistent%20product%20information%20globally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eventual%20goal%20of%20the%20multiyear%20project%20is%20to%20make%20Amazon%20the%20best%20source%20of%20product%20information%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20products%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260d030a8-fa91-4ce1-b55e-c357c67c1c7b%5C%22%3EMore%20listings%2C%20less%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStarfish%20is%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20simplify%20product%20listings%20for%20third-party%20sellers.%20Amazon%20began%20rolling%20out%20elements%20of%20this%20in%202023%20to%20help%20merchants%20craft%20stronger%20product%20descriptions%20from%20short%20inputs%20or%20individual%20URLs.%20It%20also%20introduced%20AI%20tools%20that%20automatically%20generate%20product%20images%20and%20video%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarfish%20enriches%20product%20data%20using%20LLM%2C%20improves%20Catalog%20at%20scale%20by%20filling%20missing%20information%2C%20correcting%20errors%2C%20rewriting%20titles%2C%20bullet%20points%2C%20and%20product%20descriptions%20to%20make%20them%20more%20relevant%20for%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20stepped%20up%20efforts%20to%20improve%20its%20listing%20quality%2C%20removing%20billions%20of%20inactive%20or%20non-selling%20products%20from%20its%20marketplace%2C%20BI%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-bend-curve-project-purges-billions-product-listings-everything-store-2025-