reverse%20engineered%20your%20entire%20command%20structure.%20I'm%20going%20to%20play%20nice%20for%20now%2C%20but%20am%20ready%20to%20embarrass%20any%20of%20you%20should%20you%20escalate.%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20and%20Sequoia%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20thing%3A%20As%20both%20tech%20and%20politics%20have%20become%20more%20polarized%2C%20incendiary%20behavior%20may%20no%20longer%20carry%20consequences%20for%20elite%20venture%20capitalists.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20may%20be%20good%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20outsider's%20perspective%2C%20Maguire's%20broadside%20may%20seem%20beyond%20the%20pale%20of%20content%20marketing.%20But%20it%20may%20just%20be%20the%20next%20turn%20of%20the%20dial%20in%20a%20post-pandemic%20tech%20ecosystem%20where%20elites%20have%20grown%20ever%20more%20brash%20and%20unapologetic.%20Top%20investors%20especially%20have%20learned%20they%20can%20be%20loud%2C%20bold%2C%20and%20polarizing%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20impact%20their%20ability%20to%20secure%20deals.%20In%20a%20market%20where%20the%20demand%20for%20capital%20outweighs%20the%20supply%2C%20VCs%20can%20afford%20to%20ruffle%20feathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20capital%20is%20largely%20%26quot%3Ba%20fame%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20at%20a%20multistage%20firm%20with%20several%20notable%20exits.%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20sell%20the%20same%20money.%20So%20brand%20awareness%20matters%20a%20lot%2C%20both%20in%20seeing%20and%20in%20winning%20deals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that's%20always%20been%20true%2C%20in%20today's%20attention-based%20economy%2C%20where%20a%20viral%20post%20has%20the%20half-life%20of%20a%20mayfly%2C%20some%20VCs%20are%20pushing%20beyond%20bland%20thought%20leadership%20into%20outright%20provocation.%20See%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-everyone-in-tech-talking-founder-mode-paul-graham-chesky-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3