ia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752113902-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752113902-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752113902-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-466947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJyothika%E2%80%99s%20character%20gives%20voice%20to%20the%20emotional%20cruelty%20of%20silence%20in%20a%20marriage%20built%20on%20denial.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20begins%20with%20an%20election%20campaign%2C%20but%20the%20real%20narrative%20unfolds%20when%20Omana%20unexpectedly%20files%20for%20divorce%2C%20a%20year%20after%20Article%20368%20is%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%3F%20Mathew%20is%20gay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20avoids%20melodramatic%20clich%C3%A9s%20and%20scandal-driven%20storytelling%2C%20instead%20offering%20a%20quiet%2C%20deeply%20personal%20account%20of%20a%20marriage%20built%20on%20compromise%20and%20silenced%20truths.%20Its%20power%20lies%20in%20the%20subtle%20gestures%2C%20long%20pauses%2C%20and%20emotionally%20charged%20silences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20quiet%20cultural%20earthquake%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20film%20is%20a%20courageous%20step%20forward%2C%20especially%20in%20South%20India%2C%20where%20conversations%20around%20LGBTQ%2B%20identities%20are%20still%20nascent%2C%20particularly%20among%20older%20generations%20and%20in%20rural%20communities.%20It%20made%20its%20subtle%20yet%20distinct%20mark%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeo%20Baby%2C%20the%20director%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20movie%20was%20released%2C%20many%20people%20from%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20and%20their%20families%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20saying%20the%20movie%20helped%20them%20come%20out%20to%20their%20families.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20movie%20about%20pride%20parades%20or%20rebellion%3B%20it%20is%20about%20the%20quiet%20violence%20of%20conformity%20and%20the%20invisible%20ache%20of%20suppressed%20identity.%20That%20it%20features%20Mammootty%2C%20a%20titan%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%2C%20in%20the%20lead%20is%20significant.%20For%20a%20mainstream%20hero%20of%20his%20stature%20to%20play%20a%20closeted%20gay%20man%20in%20his%20sixties%20is%20both%20a%20risk%20and%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mammootty%E2%80%99s%20portrayal%20of%20a%20closeted%20gay%20man%20is%20a%20landmark%20moment%20in%20mainstream%20Malayalam%20cinema.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1752113980-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-466950%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMammootty%E2%80%99s%20portrayal%20of%20a%20closeted%20gay%20man%20is%20a%20landmark%20moment%20in%20mainstream%20Malayalam%20cinema.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20touches%20upon%20the%20role%20of%20family%20members%20and%20the%20consequences%20they%20have%20to%20face.%20Omana%2C%20the%20wife%2C%20files%20a%20case%20for%20divorce%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20cruelty.%20The%20cruelty%20of%20being%20denied%20affection%20from%20a%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20women%20who%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20after%20the%20movie%20was%20released%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20were%20in%20the%20same%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jeo%20Baby%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brilliance%20of%20Jeo%20Baby%E2%80%99s%20direction%20lies%20in%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20sensationalise.%20There%20are%20no%20dramatic%20%E2%80%9Ccoming%20out%E2%80%9D%20speeches.%20There%20is%20no%20physical%20intimacy%20shown.%20Instead%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20emotional%20cost%3A%20the%20longing%20in%20Mathew%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20as%20he%20speaks%20of%20his%20college%20love%3B%20the%20hurt%20in%20Omana%E2%80%99s%20voice%20as%20she%20asks%20if%20her%20whole%20life%20was%20a%20lie%3B%20the%20confusion%20of%20their%20daughter%2C%20who%20realises%20her%20family%20may%20never%20have%20been%20what%20it%20seemed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20placing%20this%20story%20within%20a%20middle-class%20Christian%20family%20in%20central%20Kerala%2C%20a%20setting%20that%20traditionally%20upholds%20patriarchal%20and%20heteronormative%20values%2C%20the%20film%20forces%20its%20audience%20to%20confront%20how%20deep-rooted%20cultural%20norms%20can%20suffocate%20individuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20step%20forward%20for%20regional%20cinema%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaathal%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Core%20%3C%2Fem%3Edoesn%E2%80%99t%20pretend%20to%20offer%20solutions.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20promise%20happy%20endings.%20But%20it%20opens%20a%20door.%20It%20creates%20space%20for%20conversations%20that%20have%20long%20been%20silenced%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20drawing%20rooms%20and%20tea%20shops.%20It%20challenges%20the%20idea%20that%20queerness%20is%20incompatible%20with%20traditional%20Indian%20values%2C%20asking%20instead%3A%20What%20happen